<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Nouveau ticket de support</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <style>
        body, table, td, a {
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        }
        table, td {
            mso-table-lspace: 0pt;
            mso-table-rspace: 0pt;
        }
        img {
            -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
        }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            width: 100% !important;
            height: 100% !important;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
        }
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4f46e5, #6366f1);
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 25px;
            color: #374151;
        }
        .content h2 {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #111827;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .field {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .field strong {
            display: block;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f9fafb;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #6366f1;
        }
        .file-box {
            background-color: #eef2ff;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #4f46e5;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üì© Nouveau ticket de support</h1>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="content">
        <p>Un nouvel utilisateur a soumis un formulaire de support.</p>

        {% if user_email %}
            <div class="field">
                <strong>Adresse e-mail</strong>
                <span>{{ user_email }}</span>
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if form.subject is defined %}
            <div class="field">
                <strong>Sujet</strong>
                <span>{{ form.subject }}</span>
            </div>
        {% endif %}

        {% if form.message is defined %}
            <div class="field">
                <strong>Message</strong>
                <p>{{ form.message|nl2br }}</p>
            </div>
        {% endif %}
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
        Cet e-mail a √©t√© envoy√© automatiquement par le syst√®me de support.<br>
        Merci de ne pas y r√©pondre directement.
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
